{
  "video_id": "HQqN_d0tzYg",
  "title": "Understanding Universal Basic Income | Susan Danziger | TEDxUniversityofRochester",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Michele Gianella"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15960.0,
      "end_time": 17240.0,
      "text": "A few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17240.0,
      "end_time": 20459.0,
      "text": "I was having breakfast with my husband in the kitchen."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21140.0,
      "end_time": 26900.0,
      "text": "And up from our basement guestroom appear these two huge German dudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26900.0,
      "end_time": 31299.0,
      "text": "My husband, who had failed to mention that he had invited them to stay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31300.0,
      "end_time": 32319.0,
      "text": "quickly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32319.000000000004,
      "end_time": 39120.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, meet Arman and Shay. They&#39;re leaders of the UBI movement in Switzerland.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39450.0,
      "end_time": 42520.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Oh wow, that&#39;s so awesome!"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42520.0,
      "end_time": 44170.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s UBI?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 51349.0,
      "text": "Arman and Shay both said, \"Oh, that&#39;s universal basic income.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52340.0,
      "end_time": 54600.0,
      "text": "\"And that would be ... ?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54600.0,
      "end_time": 56240.0,
      "text": "\"Oh,\" they explained,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56240.0,
      "end_time": 61920.0,
      "text": "\"it&#39;s when everyone gets, say, monthly income, automatically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 61920.0,
      "end_time": 64000.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t have to work for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64000.0,
      "end_time": 69560.0,
      "text": "so they can pay for things like food, and clothing, and a place to live.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70400.0,
      "end_time": 74400.0,
      "text": "\"And so how much are we talking about here?\" I asked."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 74400.0,
      "end_time": 78740.0,
      "text": "My husband chimed in. He said, \"Oh, about $1,000 a month.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78740.0,
      "end_time": 80899.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Oh, that&#39;s pretty wild, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 80900.0,
      "end_time": 83600.0,
      "text": "But if we didn&#39;t have to work for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 83600.0,
      "end_time": 85919.0,
      "text": "wouldn&#39;t we all become slugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85920.0,
      "end_time": 91400.0,
      "text": "or binge watch Netflix or play video games all day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 91400.0,
      "end_time": 95360.0,
      "text": "Where would be the motivation and the curiosity to do things?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 95360.0,
      "end_time": 97240.0,
      "text": "Wouldn&#39;t it all be dulled?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97240.0,
      "end_time": 99440.0,
      "text": "I had tons of questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 101940.0,
      "text": "And what was the purpose of UBI?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 101940.0,
      "end_time": 104539.0,
      "text": "Why were they so enthusiastic about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105900.0,
      "end_time": 107400.0,
      "text": "So I decided to do some research."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107860.0,
      "end_time": 111760.0,
      "text": "I talked to a bunch of people, I even watched video debates."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112200.0,
      "end_time": 115700.0,
      "text": "I wanted to figure out what the deal was here."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115600.0,
      "end_time": 121500.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that UBI is a really complicated idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121500.0,
      "end_time": 124200.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s seriously controversial."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125180.0,
      "end_time": 130440.0,
      "text": "So what I did was I went on a journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131120.0,
      "end_time": 137280.0,
      "text": "And I realized that it actually had to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 137280.0,
      "end_time": 141560.0,
      "text": "with how technology was making everything cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 141940.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "See, I&#39;m a tech entrepreneur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 147680.0,
      "text": "and I realized that when I launched my video tech business"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147680.0,
      "end_time": 151560.0,
      "text": "that powers thousands of applications around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 151560.0,
      "end_time": 153170.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t do that years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 153170.0,
      "end_time": 157190.0,
      "text": "I would&#39;ve had to hire hundreds of people for what I could do now."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157970.0,
      "end_time": 160750.0,
      "text": "And technology is making things like food cheaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160750.0,
      "end_time": 166320.0,
      "text": "with vertical farms that are robotically powered"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 166320.0,
      "end_time": 170320.0,
      "text": "and making clothes cheaper with automatic knitting machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 170320.0,
      "end_time": 174900.0,
      "text": "And even 3D printing houses where we can live."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175320.0,
      "end_time": 178400.0,
      "text": "But the problem is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 178400.0,
      "end_time": 180880.0,
      "text": "although technology is making things cheaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 180880.0,
      "end_time": 182880.0,
      "text": "the reason it can do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 183440.0,
      "end_time": 186829.0,
      "text": "is because it doesn&#39;t require people to do the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 187920.0,
      "end_time": 188929.0,
      "text": "which means"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 188930.0,
      "end_time": 192940.0,
      "text": "that a massive number of people are soon going to be unemployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193800.0,
      "end_time": 197200.0,
      "text": "In fact, it turns out, a study recently said"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197200.0,
      "end_time": 203320.0,
      "text": "that 47 percent of all jobs could be lost in the next 20 years -"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 203320.0,
      "end_time": 205239.0,
      "text": "almost half the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205830.0,
      "end_time": 207510.0,
      "text": "So think about truck drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 207510.0,
      "end_time": 210790.0,
      "text": "There are three and a half million truck drivers out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 212360.0,
      "end_time": 214390.0,
      "text": "I think they&#39;re anticipating something like"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 214390.0,
      "end_time": 216850.0,
      "text": "80 percent of those truck drivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 216850.0,
      "end_time": 221670.0,
      "text": "could lose their jobs to self-driving trucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 222910.0,
      "end_time": 224620.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just blue-collar jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 224620.0,
      "end_time": 226740.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also all kinds of jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 226740.0,
      "end_time": 230000.0,
      "text": "like paralegals, or folks in the medical profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 230000.0,
      "end_time": 232840.0,
      "text": "or engineers across the board."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 234250.0,
      "end_time": 237840.0,
      "text": "Now, the folks who are speaking in favor of UBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 237840.0,
      "end_time": 242820.0,
      "text": "are saying that we need a way, when those folks are out of work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 242820.0,
      "end_time": 247680.0,
      "text": "they need a way to pay for food and clothing and a place to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 247680.0,
      "end_time": 251770.0,
      "text": "And UBI could be that income that they could get to pay for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 252890.0,
      "end_time": 255399.0,
      "text": "Now the folks against UBI are saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 258890.0,
      "text": "those numbers? They&#39;re actually misleading."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 259800.0,
      "end_time": 261480.0,
      "text": "Because what will happen is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 261480.00000000003,
      "end_time": 266520.0,
      "text": "eventually, over time, those jobs will be replaced by other jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 267120.0,
      "end_time": 270680.0,
      "text": "And they may be jobs that we can&#39;t even imagine today."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 271200.0,
      "end_time": 273789.0,
      "text": "So for instance, 20 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 273790.0,
      "end_time": 275920.0,
      "text": "we never even imagined"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 275920.0,
      "end_time": 277870.0,
      "text": "that there would be jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 282330.0,
      "end_time": 285150.0,
      "text": "like UX designers or app developers."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 287600.0,
      "end_time": 289800.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re saying, we don&#39;t have to worry about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289800.0,
      "end_time": 292910.0,
      "text": "Well, I actually think that we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 293110.0,
      "end_time": 296240.0,
      "text": "because we need to figure out the way, in the transition -"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 296240.0,
      "end_time": 301350.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s going to be this transition period where we have to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 301350.0,
      "end_time": 306710.0,
      "text": "how people are going to be able to eat and pay for places to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 307440.0,
      "end_time": 309680.0,
      "text": "And how are we going to pay for this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 310840.0,
      "end_time": 317820.0,
      "text": "Turns out that if every person got, say, $10,000 a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 318980.0,
      "end_time": 323100.0,
      "text": "then it would cost about $2 trillion additionally."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 324900.0,
      "end_time": 327100.0,
      "text": "And there are lots of different ideas as to how to pay for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 327100.0,
      "end_time": 328880.0,
      "text": "For instance, folks are saying:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 328880.0,
      "end_time": 331250.0,
      "text": "Look, we don&#39;t need our whole welfare system"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 331250.0,
      "end_time": 332530.0,
      "text": "or maybe any of it at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 332530.0,
      "end_time": 334719.0,
      "text": "because UBI will replace it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 338480.0,
      "text": "Things like food stamps and homeless shelters will go away"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 338480.0,
      "end_time": 341560.0,
      "text": "because people will be able to pay for food and housing."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 342290.0,
      "end_time": 345680.0,
      "text": "Other people are saying: Well, we can make cuts in the military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 345680.0,
      "end_time": 348400.0,
      "text": "or we can add income tax to the rich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 348400.0,
      "end_time": 352433.0,
      "text": "or maybe carbon tax for corporations that hurt the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 352434.0,
      "end_time": 353720.0,
      "text": "Some people are even saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 353720.0,
      "end_time": 356693.0,
      "text": "we could print money because it&#39;s a whole new economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 357733.0,
      "end_time": 360200.0,
      "text": "Or maybe a combination of all of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 362940.0,
      "end_time": 364700.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have an answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 364700.0,
      "end_time": 366180.0,
      "text": "and I don&#39;t think anybody really understands"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 366180.0,
      "end_time": 368160.0,
      "text": "or has an answer at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 368160.0,
      "end_time": 372800.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m an entrepreneur, and when I start a company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 372510.0,
      "end_time": 375130.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have to figure out how it&#39;s all going to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 375130.0,
      "end_time": 379000.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t go from 1 to 100 overnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 379000.0,
      "end_time": 381640.0,
      "text": "It takes phases and experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 381640.0,
      "end_time": 385700.0,
      "text": "and we start little by little, and we figure it out as we go along."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 386280.0,
      "end_time": 389400.0,
      "text": "So I wondered if experiments were happening with UBI."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 390770.0,
      "end_time": 394840.0,
      "text": "And then I met Mikael and Johannes, two other German dudes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 395820.0,
      "end_time": 400900.0,
      "text": "and they told me about experiments that were happening all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 400720.0,
      "end_time": 404470.0,
      "text": "There are experiments happening in Kenya, and it was wild."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 404470.0,
      "end_time": 409440.0,
      "text": "They said that 90 percent of all UBI recipients"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 409440.0,
      "end_time": 413110.0,
      "text": "actually started businesses with it or bought livestock."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 415000.0,
      "end_time": 419840.0,
      "text": "Mikael and Johannes actually started their own UBI experiment out of Berlin."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 420600.0,
      "end_time": 421860.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re crowdfunding it."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 421860.0,
      "end_time": 424800.0,
      "text": "So what they&#39;re doing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 424800.0,
      "end_time": 427880.0,
      "text": "each time they raise about 12,000 euros or so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 428340.0,
      "end_time": 431450.0,
      "text": "then they hold a completely random lottery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 431450.0,
      "end_time": 434370.0,
      "text": "anybody can participate, even you guys here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 434950.0,
      "end_time": 438400.0,
      "text": "and the winner gets 1,000 euros a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 438400.0,
      "end_time": 440560.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s about $1,000 a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 440560.0,
      "end_time": 441942.0,
      "text": "No strings attached."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 441942.0,
      "end_time": 444920.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to say what you&#39;re going to do with the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 444920.0,
      "end_time": 447110.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to say what you&#39;ve done with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 447110.0,
      "end_time": 451280.0,
      "text": "And the winners, it turns out, also started a number of businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 451280.0,
      "end_time": 455440.0,
      "text": "There was one woman who started a funeral service business."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 455750.0,
      "end_time": 458120.0,
      "text": "She goes around at funerals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 458120.0,
      "end_time": 461770.0,
      "text": "and she says nice things about the recently deceased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 461770.0,
      "end_time": 463849.0,
      "text": "and gets paid for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 463850.0,
      "end_time": 465600.0,
      "text": "Pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 465520.0,
      "end_time": 466599.0,
      "text": "I know as a founder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 466600.0,
      "end_time": 469590.0,
      "text": "it takes a lot of time and months and months"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 469590.0,
      "end_time": 471719.0,
      "text": "to figure out product-market fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 471720.0,
      "end_time": 475400.0,
      "text": "It took us about 18 months for Ziggeo, my company."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 475560.0,
      "end_time": 478270.0,
      "text": "And I could see how having UBI in the background,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 478270.0,
      "end_time": 480840.0,
      "text": "knowing you can eat and have a place to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 480840.0,
      "end_time": 483390.0,
      "text": "while you&#39;re figuring it all out"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 483400.0,
      "end_time": 486920.0,
      "text": "could be the difference between persevering and failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 489000.0,
      "end_time": 493770.0,
      "text": "All of this talk about UBI made me think about my own life."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 494470.0,
      "end_time": 496850.0,
      "text": "See, I wasn&#39;t always a tech entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 497320.0,
      "end_time": 501599.0,
      "text": "In fact, I originally studied art history, focusing on the Renaissance -"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 501600.0,
      "end_time": 504540.0,
      "text": "you know, Michelangelo and Leonardo Da Vinci."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 505600.0,
      "end_time": 510300.0,
      "text": "They painted the Sistine Chapel and The Last Supper."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 510390.0,
      "end_time": 513720.0,
      "text": "And they were able to do it because they had patrons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 513720.0,
      "end_time": 517320.0,
      "text": "like Pope Julius the Second and the Medicis."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 518520.0,
      "end_time": 520780.0,
      "text": "I, unfortunately, was not as lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 521700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523170.00000000006,
      "text": "I did not have a patron."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 523500.0,
      "end_time": 526600.0,
      "text": "And I didn&#39;t have any particular talents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 526600.0,
      "end_time": 528500.0,
      "text": "well, except maybe ping pong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 528500.0,
      "end_time": 531329.0,
      "text": "but I didn&#39;t think that was going to pay the bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 532240.0,
      "end_time": 534940.0,
      "text": "So I had to figure out a way to make a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 535330.0,
      "end_time": 539250.0,
      "text": "I decided to go to law school and become a lawyer."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 540000.0,
      "end_time": 544180.0,
      "text": "The problem is, I was never particularly interested in the law."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 544790.0,
      "end_time": 546439.0,
      "text": "And once I became a lawyer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 546440.0,
      "end_time": 547992.0,
      "text": "I spent years and years"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 547992.0,
      "end_time": 551699.0,
      "text": "toiling in a profession that I wasn&#39;t particularly interested in."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 552910.0,
      "end_time": 557000.0,
      "text": "I wondered if I had gotten UBI, that $1,000 a month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 557000.0,
      "end_time": 560000.0,
      "text": "growing up or as a young adult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 560000.0,
      "end_time": 563600.0,
      "text": "whether I would&#39;ve started businesses sooner."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 563460.0,
      "end_time": 564780.0,
      "text": "Probably."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 565460.0,
      "end_time": 567520.0,
      "text": "And would I have gone to law school?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 567910.0,
      "end_time": 569110.0,
      "text": "I doubt it."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 569700.0,
      "end_time": 573480.0,
      "text": "I wondered if my friends were in the same boat as I was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 573480.0,
      "end_time": 577200.0,
      "text": "so I decided to launch a survey that a number of you took."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 578640.0,
      "end_time": 580400.0,
      "text": "And I asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 580920.0,
      "end_time": 583260.0,
      "text": "if you knew as a teenager"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 583850.0,
      "end_time": 589600.0,
      "text": "that you would be given $1,000 a month, guaranteed for life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 590900.0,
      "end_time": 592900.0,
      "text": "would you have made different choices?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 594770.0,
      "end_time": 599720.0,
      "text": "And I got 576 responses in just a few days. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 601300.0,
      "end_time": 603510.0,
      "text": "And the results were fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 604390.0,
      "end_time": 606750.0,
      "text": "What I found was that I wasn&#39;t alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 607700.0,
      "end_time": 610720.0,
      "text": "that there were so many people who would&#39;ve taken risks"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 610720.0,
      "end_time": 614770.0,
      "text": "and would&#39;ve followed their passions had they had that money."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 615550.0,
      "end_time": 617439.0,
      "text": "There was a woman who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 617440.0,
      "end_time": 621200.0,
      "text": "that the money would&#39;ve given her the confidence to be bold."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 622320.0,
      "end_time": 625280.0,
      "text": "Another who said that she couldn&#39;t afford to take risks"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 625280.0,
      "end_time": 629790.0,
      "text": "because failure would&#39;ve meant no food on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 630570.0,
      "end_time": 631840.0,
      "text": "I had hundreds of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 631840.0,
      "end_time": 634570.0,
      "text": "respond that they would&#39;ve traveled more"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 634570.0,
      "end_time": 636490.0,
      "text": "or lived independently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 637270.0,
      "end_time": 638270.0,
      "text": "people who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 638270.0,
      "end_time": 642480.0,
      "text": "that they wouldn&#39;t have moved in with their boyfriends"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 642480.0,
      "end_time": 644820.0,
      "text": "or gotten married so young."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 645640.0,
      "end_time": 646900.0,
      "text": "There were people who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 646900.0,
      "end_time": 649300.0,
      "text": "that they would&#39;ve taken more maternity leave"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 649300.0,
      "end_time": 651520.0,
      "text": "or spent more time at home with their kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 651880.0,
      "end_time": 652950.0,
      "text": "A guy who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 652950.0,
      "end_time": 655890.0,
      "text": "that he would&#39;ve spent time with his sick mother;"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 655890.0,
      "end_time": 656900.0,
      "text": "and a woman who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 656900.0,
      "end_time": 661510.0,
      "text": "that she would&#39;ve spent more time with her terminally ill husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 663720.0,
      "end_time": 666970.0,
      "text": "But not everybody was so positive about that $1,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 666970.0,
      "end_time": 669400.0,
      "text": "There was a guy who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 669400.0,
      "end_time": 672610.0,
      "text": "that he would have burned through it in college bars."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 673120.0,
      "end_time": 675400.0,
      "text": "And another woman who said"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 675400.0,
      "end_time": 678690.0,
      "text": "that she would&#39;ve pissed through it on material things."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 680280.0,
      "end_time": 684480.0,
      "text": "And then there was one women who said that she was a teenage drug addict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 684480.0,
      "end_time": 685800.0,
      "text": "and that automatic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 685800.0,
      "end_time": 688329.0,
      "text": "would&#39;ve probably been the worst thing for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 690440.0,
      "end_time": 697400.0,
      "text": "I heard from musicians and artists and opera singers and theater directors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 697400.0,
      "end_time": 699720.0,
      "text": "all of whom had given up their passions"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 699720.0,
      "end_time": 703560.0,
      "text": "to become bankers and lawyers and engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 704720.0,
      "end_time": 707470.0,
      "text": "Now, there were certainly those who had passions for that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 707470.0,
      "end_time": 711300.0,
      "text": "and that was wonderful, and the UBI would&#39;ve helped them as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 712390.0,
      "end_time": 715800.0,
      "text": "But time and time again, I heard of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 715800.0,
      "end_time": 717680.0,
      "text": "who said that they lost three years of their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 717680.0,
      "end_time": 719699.0,
      "text": "ten years of their life and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 719700.0,
      "end_time": 724400.0,
      "text": "working in crappy jobs or professions that they had absolutely no interest in."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 726100.0,
      "end_time": 728120.0,
      "text": "And for me, that&#39;s the worst."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 728120.0,
      "end_time": 730440.0,
      "text": "That time, that precious time -"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 730440.0,
      "end_time": 734560.0,
      "text": "actually, the most precious thing that we have - lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 734560.0,
      "end_time": 738619.0,
      "text": "wasted years, not focusing on the things that they love."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 740670.0,
      "end_time": 743729.0,
      "text": "I wonder whether if we had UBI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 744500.0,
      "end_time": 746880.0,
      "text": "whether we could focus on the passions."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 746880.0,
      "end_time": 750520.0,
      "text": "Whether we could spend more time with the folks that we love."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 750520.0,
      "end_time": 752000.0,
      "text": "Whether we might jump start"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 752000.0,
      "end_time": 756200.0,
      "text": "an entire renaissance of artists and painters and sculptors."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 756200.0,
      "end_time": 758840.0,
      "text": "Whether in fact UBI could be our new patrons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 758840.0,
      "end_time": 765560.0,
      "text": "just as Michelangelo and Leonardo had Julius the Second and the Medicis."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 768820.0,
      "end_time": 770370.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s not get hung up"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 770370.0,
      "end_time": 773960.0,
      "text": "on whether we&#39;re going to have jobs in 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 774750.0,
      "end_time": 777470.0,
      "text": "or how much UBI is going to cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 778920.0,
      "end_time": 780860.0,
      "text": "Those are mere distractions."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 782360.0,
      "end_time": 786700.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s focus on the questions that really matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 790500.0,
      "end_time": 795690.0,
      "text": "Questions like: Can we spend the time on things we&#39;re passionate about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 797400.0,
      "end_time": 801630.0,
      "text": "Do we have to take the job or go to law school to become a lawyer"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 801850.0,
      "end_time": 803680.0,
      "text": "just because we think"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 803680.0,
      "end_time": 807449.0,
      "text": "we have to pay the bills and find a way to make a living?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 809000.0,
      "end_time": 813400.0,
      "text": "If we have an idea, can we find creative ways in which to fund it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 813600.0,
      "end_time": 819320.0,
      "text": "Can things like Patreon and Kickstarter be our new personal basic income?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 820460.0,
      "end_time": 822800.0,
      "text": "And as we raise our children"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 822800.0,
      "end_time": 827260.0,
      "text": "in a world that values money more than meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 828720.0,
      "end_time": 830240.0,
      "text": "how can we teach them"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 830240.0,
      "end_time": 834710.0,
      "text": "to follow their passions and hearts and focus on what interests them most?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 835680.0,
      "end_time": 838319.0,
      "text": "These are the questions I&#39;m curious about."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 838790.0,
      "end_time": 842100.0,
      "text": "These are the questions that empower me every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 842380.0,
      "end_time": 846810.0,
      "text": "I hope that these questions and the answers empower you as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 847850.0,
      "end_time": 850760.0,
      "text": "And I hope together, we can build a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 850760.0,
      "end_time": 853600.0,
      "text": "in which we have the confidence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 853340.0,
      "end_time": 854790.0,
      "text": "and income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 855220.0,
      "end_time": 857560.0,
      "text": "to go where curiosity takes us."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 858260.0,
      "end_time": 859590.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 859590.0,
      "end_time": 861120.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}